title: Urban Meyer to Jacksonville and Robert Saleh to the Jets Plus, Divisional-Round Bets
description:
Warren Sharp and Joe House react to the news that Urban Meyer will be the next head coach of the Jacksonville Jaguars. They discuss the biggest questions remaining for the Jaguars (02:30) and former 49ers defensive coordinator Robert Saleh signing with Jets, (59:42) and then they dive into this weekend’s divisional round (28:30).

Hosts: Warren Sharp and Joe House
